export const DonationStatus = {
    NEW:"new",
    ON_PROGRESS:"on-progress",
    COLLECTED:"collected",
    COMPLETED:"completed",
    CANCELLED:"cancelled"
}

    [DonationStatus.NEW]:"Waiting for accept",

    [DonationStatus.CANCELLED]:"Donation cancelled"
}
